text.tspan: You must provide the certificate of completion
to your ethics counselor in your servicing legal
office to get credit for completing this training.
This website provides training support for
completion of annual requirement, but is not
affiliated with the FDM system that sends
reminders for you completion status. Your
ethics counselor will update your status in FDM
in order to get credit for completed training.
